comment:
 A nicer default set of colors than the ones CSS ships with. Color codes taken from [clrs.cc](http://clrs.cc).

    import Css.Colors exposing (..)

    stylesheet
      [ button
          [ backgroundColor blue ]
      ]

...compiles to:

    button {
        backgroundColor: #0074D9;
    }

